items.badge_description: At a new place and don't want to choose a pint of something you may not like? Grab a few tasters! Enjoy some small pours and then decide which to upgrade to a full pour. That's 275 checkins with the serving style of Taster. Try 5 more for Level 56! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast
